data.description:
Beautiful Graham Hart home, who built this home with a kitchen that inspires cooking and entertaining. Open to a spacious vaulted ceiling family room that boasts a wall of windows for natural light, pre-wired for surround sound. This home has 2 downstairs master suites that can be used as a guest room or used by grandparents; extended 2.5 car garage. Private oversized backyard with covered patio, ceiling fans and plenty of room for a pool. The neighborhood backs up to Champions Circle Golf Course and has 2 community pools and tons of parks in the area.  Near Texas Motor Speedway, and tons of entertainment, Buckee's, and an outdoor shopping mall!
COMING SOON! PROFESSIONAL PHOTOS!
